db:section.db:title: [noexcept, since 5.5] uint qHash(QSslEllipticCurve curve, uint seed = 0)
db:section.db:para: Returns an hash value for the curve curve, using seed to seed the calculation.
This function was introduced in Qt 5.5.

db:section.db:title: [noexcept, since 5.4] uint qHash(const QSslCertificate &key, uint seed = 0)
db:section.db:para: Returns the hash value for the key, using seed to seed the calculation.
This function was introduced in Qt 5.4.

db:section.db:title: [noexcept, since 5.4] uint qHash(const QSslError &key, uint seed = 0)
db:section.db:para: Returns the hash value for the key, using seed to seed the calculation.
This function was introduced in Qt 5.4.
